value.excerpt: A really fun series of professional StarCraft 2 between PartinG and Cure. In this best-of-3 we see a variety of openers from both players and in two of them, Cure goes for a timing attack where he's building structures like Bunkers on his opponent's side of the map. value.title: StarCraft 2: The ULTIMATE LATE GAME of Zerg vs Zerg! (Dark vs Reynor)
value.excerpt: One long macro game of StarCraft 2 between Dark and Reynor. While most Zerg versus Zerg games end within a few minutes, this one goes well beyond the Zergling Baneling, Roach Ravager and even the Hydra Lurker stage.
